It is understood and agreed that participation in programs contemplated will be coordinated and implemented through XU and SCAC and will cover activities related to the teaching and study of French language. French and Filipino culture and scientific endeavors;

It is further understood and agreed that coordination and implementation of ich programs as may be created will be covered by specific Executive Agreemer , be subsequently drawn up and signed by the duly-authorized representatives

ARTICLE TWO

XU and SCAC agree to exert their best efforts to achieve the following forms of cooperation:

1. Participation in education, training, meetings and seminars upon the invitation of the institution organizing the activity;

2. Exchange of expertise and information in teaching programs as well as in late- breaking developments in methods and techniques of language pedagogy;

3. Assistance in the development of new areas of activities and manpower in those areas for the benefit of the institutions and the provinces of Northern

Mindanao in general;

4. Collaborative actions for the promotion of French cultural heritage in Northern

Mindanao through exhibits, film festivals, lectures;

5. Joint efforts in carrying out a program of students' and faculty mobility between French institutions and XU;

XU agrees to exert its best effort to achieve the following forms of cooperation:

1. Maintain French courses in its curriculum for its Bachelor of Arts in

International Studies and offer it as an elective in other programs;

2. Offer regular and tutorial classes in French for non XU students;

3. Disseminate information on the different programs of the French government in educational, cultural and scientific cooperation

4. Promote exchange with French academic institutions for reciprocal benefit;

5. Be the venue for activities organized by SCAC in Northern Mindanao promoting

